Comics comprise the majority of zines in this archive because those were the communities I was involved with. As such it‚Äôs an unweildy category in need of breaking down but for now it comprises publications that are analogous to a comic book or graphic novel, usually containing a main story and anchored by one or two people. Some will have zine-y features, such as articles, inteviews, letters and reviews, while others will have just the story between covers. Some will be serialised over many issues, other stand alone. Contrast with Anthology comics.
